an%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20number%20of%20delayed%20projects%20related%20to%20infrastructure%20development%20in%20the%20railways%20had%20increased%20from%2056%20in%202022%20to%2098%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%2024%20infrastructure%20sectors%2C%20railways%20ranks%20second%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20projects%20delayed.%20Road%20transport%20and%20highways%20sector%20stands%20first%2C%20that%20report%20has%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20government%20had%20said%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20that%20delays%20in%20more%20than%20800%20government%20projects%20led%20to%20cost%20overruns%20of%20Rs%204.5%20trillion%20as%20of%20December%202022.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Feconomy-policy%2Fdelays-in-over-800-projects-cost-government-over-rs-4-5-trillion-123020801209_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehad%20reported%20on%20this%20reply%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20government%20had%20planned%201%2C438%20projects%20with%20an%20original%20cost%20of%20Rs%2020.4%20trillion.%20Their%20cost%20has%20increased%20to%20Rs%2024.9%20trillion%20as%20of%20December%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708323966000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16130341%2F19351115534_6b836e91b8_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fover-840-railway-projects-delayed-by-an-average-of-36-months-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20report%20on%20Hindu%20Businessline%20says%20that%20the%20delay%20results%20in%20an%20anticipated%20completion%20cost%20which%20is%20over%2018.5%25%20higher%20than%20the%20original%20cost.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fover-840-railway-projects-delayed-by-an-average-of-36-months-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22t