a%2C%20Russia%20has%20never%20invaded%20a%20NATO%20country%20because%20Russia%20has%20typically%20been%20very%20intimidated%20by%20this%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20North%20Atlantic%20Treaty%20Organization%20(NATO)%20is%20an%20intergovernmental%20military%20alliance%20of%2031%20member%20states%20%E2%80%93%2029%20European%20and%20two%20North%20American.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20China%20is%20intimidated%20by%20this%20alliance.%20So%2C%20keeping%20NATO%20strong%20is%20important%2C%20Haley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaley%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20remarks%20by%20Trump%20in%20South%20Carolina%20a%20week%20ago%20that%20he%20would%20encourage%20Russia%20to%20do%20%E2%80%9Cwhatever%20the%20hell%20they%20want%E2%80%9D%20to%20any%20NATO%20member%20country%20that%20doesn't%20meet%20spending%20guidelines%20on%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20more%20friends%20to%20the%20fold%20is%20important.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20time%20to%20leave%20an%20alliance.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20time%20to%20side%20with%20a%20thug%20and%20not%20side%20with%20friends%2C%20who%20stood%20with%20America%20after%20the%20September%2011%20attacks%2C%20Haley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20stand%20firm.%20Because%20when%20we%20stand%20firm%20with%20our%20friends%2C%20our%20enemies%20stay%20on%20their%20heels.%20When%20we%20start%20to%20show%20any%20weakening%20of%20those%20alliances%2C%20that's%20when%20our%20enemies%20move.%20That's%20why%20we're%20seeing%20China%20on%20the%20march.%20That's%20why%20we're%20seeing%20Iran%20want%20to%20build%20a%20nuclear%20bomb.%20That's%20why%20we're%20seeing%20Russia%20start%20to%20move%20towards%20Poland%20and%20the%20Baltics%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20what%20I%20promise%20I%20will%20do%20as%20president%2C%20is%20we%20not%20only%20will%20strengthen%20NATO%2C%20we%20will%20strengthen%20alliances%20with%20India%2C%20Australia%2C%20Japan%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20the%20Philippines.%20We%20will%20add%20to%20the%20fold.%20This%20is%20about%20America%20having%20more%20friends%2C%20not%20less%20friends%2C%E2%80%9D%20Haley%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaley%20called%20Trump's%20NATO%20comments%20%E2%80%9Cbone-chilling%E2%80%9D%20and%20empowering%20to%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20all%20he%20did%20in%20that%20moment%20was%2C%20he%20sided%20with%20a%20guy%20who%20kills%20his%20political%20opponents%2C%20he%20sided%20with%20a%20thug%20who%20arrests%20American%20journalists%20and%20holds%20them%20hostage%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaley%20alleged%20that%20incumbent%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20a%20Democrat%2C%20has%20also%20failed%20on%20multiple%20fronts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20has%20emboldened%20our%20enemies.%20That's%20why%20you%20see%20them%20moving.%20It%20happened%20after%20the%20fall%20of%20Afghanistan.%20It%20is%20continuing%20to%20happen.%20Then%20they%20go%20and%20they%20see%20the%20other%20opponent%20running%20for%20-%20for%20president%20and%20they%20see%20that%20he%20doesn't%20worry%20about%20Putin%20invading%20Ukraine.%20So%2C%20what%20does%20Putin%20do%3F%20He%20goes%20and%20now%20he's%20starting%20to%20put%20soldiers%20around%20the%20Baltics.%20He's%20moving%20in%20for%20the%20next%20era%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet's%20remind%20the%20American%20people%20that%20Putin%20said%20once%20he%20takes%20Ukraine%2C%20Poland%20and%20the%20Baltics%20are%20next.%20Now%20he%20is%20putting%20soldiers%20around%20those%20countries%2C%20just%20like%20he%20did%20Ukraine.%20And%20if%20that%20happens%2C%20those%20are%20NATO%20countries.%20That%20immediately%20puts%20America%20at%20war.%20That%20is%20what%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20avoid.%20And%20that's%20why%20this%20aid%20package%20is%20so%20important%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20f