uns%20in%20three%20Tests%40109.00%2C%20with%20two%20double%20centuries%20and%20one%20fifty%20-%20by%20far%20the%20most%20by%20any%20batsman%20in%20the%20India-England%20five-Test%20series.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22GAURAV%20GUPTA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fengland-in-india%2Ffrom-tent-to-triumph-yashasvi-jaiswals-rise-continues%2Farticleshow%2F107808569.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20MSP%20Guarantee%20Law%2C%20Centre%20Tables%20Proposal%20to%20Buy%205%20Crops%20at%20MSP%20for%205%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16094318%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-9.40.47-AM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20the%20first%20time%20since%20negotiations%20began%20with%20farmers%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20tabled%20a%20key%20proposal%20before%20farmer%20leaders%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20a%20minimum%20support%20price%20guarantee%2C%20during%20the%20fourth%20round%20of%20talks%20here%2C%20late%20on%20February%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20of%20Union%20ministers%20proposed%20that%20government%20agencies%20would%20buy%20three%20pulse%20crops%2C%20maize%2C%20and%20cotton%20at%20MSP%20for%20five%20years%20after%20entering%20into%20a%20legal%20contract%20with%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20promoted%20cooperative%20societies%20like%20NCCF%20(National%20Cooperative%20Consumers%E2%80%99%20Federation%20of%20India)%20and%20NAFED%20(National%20Agricultural%20Cooperative%20Marketing%20Federation%20of%20India)%20will%20form%20a%20contract%20for%20the%20next%205%20years%20and%20buy%20products%20from%20the%20farmers%20on%20MSP.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20limit%20on%20the%20quantity%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Union%20commerce%20minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20after%20a%20meeting%20with%20farmers%20that%20lasted%20late%20till%201.30%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20agriculture%20minister%20Arjun%20Munda%20and%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Home%20Affairs%20Nityanand%20Rai%20were%20also%20present%20at%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20proposal%20was%20not%20something%20farmers%20had%20been%20expecting%20or%20gunning%20for%20as%20they%20had%20wanted%20a%20law%20on%20MSP%20which%20would%20provide%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20to%20all%2023%20crops%20of%20which%20the%20Union%20government%20decides%20MSP%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20why%20farmers%20did%20not%20commit%20anything%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20on%20their%20latest%20proposal%20and%20told%20ministers%20that%20they%20would%20first%20discuss%20the%20proposal%20at%20their%20forums%20over%20the%20next%20two%20days%20and%20thereafter%2C%20decide%20the%20future%20course%20of%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%20were%20represented%20by%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%2C%20coordinator%20of%20the%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%C2%A0%20Morcha%20(KMM)%2C%20and%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%2C%20convener%20of%20SKM%20(non-political)%2C%20a%20splinter%20group%20of%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%20which%20played%20key%20role%20in%202020%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%2C%20Dallewal%20told%20reporters%20that%20they%20will%20discuss%20the%20proposal%20by%20the%20government%20with%20their%20respective%20forums%20and%20experts.%20%E2%80%9CThen%2C%20we%20will%20come%20to%20a%20conclusion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fthe-solution-to-farmers-problems-lies-in-the-macro%5C%22%3EThe%20Solution%20to%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Problems%20Lies%20in%20the%20Macro%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandher%20then%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20will%20continue%20from%20February%2021%20if%20no%20final%20result%20comes%20out%20in%20next%20two%20days.%20We%20have%20other%20demands%20apart%20from%20MSP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtesters%20have%20been%20camping%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20borders%20%E2%80%94%20at%20Shambhu%20barrier%20and%20Khanauri%20border%20points%20%E2%80%94%20since%20the%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20march%20began%20on%20February%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20farmer%20unions%20from%20Haryana%20had%20not%20been%20forthcoming.%20But%20on%20February%2018%2C%20Haryana%20BKU%20(Chaduni)%20chief%20Gurnam%20Singh%20Chaduni%2C%20who%20had%20key%20role%20in%202020%20farm%20protest%20too%2C%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20group%20would%20join%20the%20big%20stir%20if%20the%20talks%20between%20Punjab%20farmers%E2%80%99%20bodies%20and%20the%20Union%20government%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Punjab%20unit%20of%20the%20original%20SKM%20group%20too%20has%20decided%20to%20hold%20day%20and%20night%20mass%20protests%20in%20front%20of%20the%20houses%20of%20MPs%2C%20MLAs%2C%20ministers%20and%20district%20presidents%20of%20BJP%20for%20the%20next%20three%20days.%20The%20protest%20will%20start%20at%2010%20am%20on%20February%2020%20and%20end%20at%205%20pm%20on%20February%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SKM%20in%20a%20press%20statement%20on%20Sunday%20also%20informed%20that%20they%20would%20hold%20their%20national%20coordination%20committee%20meeting%20at%202%20pm%20on%20February%2021%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20general%20body%20next%20day%20to%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20decide%20upon%20future%20plans%20of%20action%20to%20intensify%20the%20ongoing%20struggles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20stated%20that%20commitments%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20made%20at%20the%20time%20of%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20have%20remained%20unfulfilled%2C%20be%20it%20deciding%20MSP%20at%20the%20%E2%80%98cost%20and%2050%25%E2%80%99%20model%2C%20with%20guaranteed%20procurement%2C%20the%20comprehensive%20loan%20waiver%20scheme%2C%20no%20privatisation%20of%20electricity%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20BKU%20Ugrahan%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20farmers%E2%80%99%20bodies%20in%20Punjab%20staged%20a%20dharna%20outside%20the%20residences%20of%20BJP%20state%20president%20Sunil%20Jakhar%20in%20Abohar%2C%20Captain%20Amarinder%20Singh%20in%20Patiala%2C%20and%20Kewal%20Dhillon%20in%20Barnala%20on%20Saturday%20and%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Navjot%20Singh%20Sidhu%20also%20threw%20his%20weight%20behind%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20internet%20shutdown%20was%20extended%20in%20seven%20districts%20of%20Haryana%20to%20February%2024.%20In%20Punjab%20too%2C%20six%20districts%20are%20now%20facing%20internet%20shutdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708314947000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F16094318%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-16-at-9.40.47-AM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmsp-farmers-proposal-maize-cotton-pulses%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Farmers%20have%20sought%20time%20till%20February%2020%20to%20discuss%20the%20proposal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmsp-farmers-proposal-maize-cotton-pulses%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20sets%20Ramadan%20deadline%20for%20offensive%20on%20Gazan%20city%20Rafah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708314888000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107808570%2Cimgsize-1952932.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-sets-ramadan-deadline-for-offensive-on-gazan-city-rafah%2Farticleshow%2F107808003.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107808003.cm