nd%20regional%20culture%2C%20but%20now%20it%20has%20become%20a%20'kotha'%2C%20he%20wrote%20on%20February%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20name%20of%20cultural%20events%2C%20shaking%20booty%20on%20item%20songs%20is%20all%20they%20call%20a%20cultural%20program.%20Along%20with%20the%20education%20system%2C%20the%20cultural%20system%20is%20in%20danger%20in%20India.%20What%20a%20downfall%20for%20this%20generation%20and%20colleges%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Aaryan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20later%2C%20Ms%20Parija%20commented%20on%20the%20post%2C%20which%20has%20now%20over%2025%20lakh%20views%2C%20and%20said%20that%20she%20was%20the%20girl%20in%20the%20video%20and%20that%20the%20video%20was%20reposted%20without%20her%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20take%20it%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Parija%20requested%20and%20said%20that%20she%20was%20not%20a%20student%20at%20the%20college%20but%20was%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20a%20professional%20performer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20the%20judge%20there.%20The%20students%2C%20audience%20and%20everyone%20in%20the%20auditorium%20requested%20me%20to%20perform%20on%20this%20track%20at%20their%20own%20fest%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20a%20right%20to%20voice%20what%20is%20right%20and%20what%20is%20not%20but%20not%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20defaming%20me%2C%20who%20is%20not%20even%20associated%20with%20the%20college%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Parija%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mr%20Aaryan%2C%20in%20response%2C%20said%20he%20spoke%20about%20Indian%20schools%20and%20colleges%20and%20was%20not%20pointing%20fingers%20at%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20spoke%20about%20Indian%20schools%20and%20colleges%2C%20explicitly%20stating%20that%20I%20haven't%20said%20anything%20about%20you.%20I%20haven't%20slut-shamed%20you%20(as%20you%20alleged)%20in%20any%20way.%20In%20the%20second%20line%2C%20I%20mentioned%20that%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20a