t%20network%2C%20was%20fatally%20shot%20by%20an%20unidentified%20assailant%20during%20a%20wedding%20ceremony%20in%20the%20Chung%20area%20on%20February%2018%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20a%20private%20TV%20channel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpak-gangster-ameer-balaj-tipu-shot-dead-at-lahore-wedding-report-5084768%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpak-gangster-ameer-balaj-tipu-shot-dead-at-lahore-wedding-report-5084768%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpak-gangster-ameer-balaj-tipu-shot-dead-at-lahore-wedding-report-5084768%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandigarh%3A%20BJP%20Mayor%20Resigns%20Ahead%20of%20SC%20Hearing%2C%20Power%20Likely%20to%20Remain%20with%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F19085122%2FGGoxsalWMAAEL_a-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Chandigarh%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20mayor%20Manoj%20Sonkar%20resigned%20from%20his%20post%20late%20on%20February%2018%2C%20days%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwont-allow-democracy-to-be-murdered-cji-chandrachud-on-chandigarh-stolen-mayoral-election%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20made%20scathing%20remarks%20against%20a%20presiding%20officer%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20purportedly%20rigging%20last%20month%E2%80%99s%20Chandigarh%20mayoral%20polls%20in%20Sonkar%E2%80%99s%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20asked%20Sonkar%20to%20resign%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20resumption%20of%20hearing%20on%20February%2019%20at%20the%20apex%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20hearing%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20noticeably%20slammed%20the%20way%20presiding%20officer%20Anil%20Masih%20had%20conducted%20the%20election%20in%20order%20to%20favour%20Sonkar.%20The%20court%20has%20even%20summoned%20him%20today%2C%20to%20explain%20why%20he%20defaced%20cast%20ballots%20and%20later%20declared%20them%20invalid%20in%20an%20ostensible%20effort%20to%20declare%20Sonkar%20victorious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20however%20said%20that%20BJP%20has%20not%20fully%20conceded%20defeat%20on%20this%20mayoral%20seat.%20Sources%20confirmed%20that%20three%20councillors%20of%20principal%20opposition%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20fighting%20BJP%20tooth%20and%20nail%20in%20this%20poll%20rigging%20case%20and%20had%20even%20petitioned%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20this%20regard%20%E2%80%93%20have%20now%20joined%20BJP%20in%20Delhi%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20Chandigarh%20BJP%20president%20Arun%20Sood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20joined%20BJP%20are%20Gurcharan%20Singh%20Kala%2C%20Neha%20and%20Poonam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20joining%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20would%20help%20BJP%20muster%20enough%20numbers%20ahead%20of%20what%20is%20now%20an%20imminent%20re-polling.%20The%20election%20may%20be%20announced%20anytime%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%2C%20AAP%20Chandigarh%20leader%20Prem%20Garg%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20it%20was%20unfortunate%20that%20these%20three%20councillors%20ditched%20the%20party%20at%20this%20juncture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20while%20the%20exit%20of%20the%20BJP%20mayor%20was%20imminent%20after%20the%20SC%20snub%2C%20it%20is%20ironical%20that%20BJP%20appears%20to%20have%20launched%20an%20%E2%80%98Operation%20Lotus%E2%80%99%20even%20for%20a%20city%E2%80%99s%20civic%20body%20election.%20%E2%80%98Operation%20Lotus%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20term%20for%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20horse%20trading%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20BJP%20first%20by%20rigging%20polls%20and%20now%20by%20poaching%20their%20councillors%20had%20proved%20that%20it%20could%20stoop%20to%20any%20low%20to%20seize%20power%20by%20unfair%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGarg%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20BJP%20can%20do%20anything%20for%20a%20small%20election%2C%20imagine%20what%20it%20can%20do%20in%20bigger%20elections%3F%20This%2C%20in%20true%20sense%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmurder-of-democracy-supreme-court-chandigarh-narendra-modi-anil-massih%5C%22%3Emurder%20of%20democracy%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20the%20numbers%20say%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20induction%20of%20the%20three%20AAP%20councillors%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%2014%20councillors%2C%20Congress%20had%20seven%2C%20and%20AAP%20had%2013%20in%20the%2035-member%20Chandigarh%20Municipal%20Corporation%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20remaining%20councillor%20belonged%20to%20former%20BJP%20ally%20Akali%20Dal.%20There%20is%20one%20additional%20vote%20of%20a%20Chandigarh%20MP%2C%20who%20is%20the%20ex-officio%20member%20of%20the%20House.%20Currently%2C%20that%20is%20BJP%20MP%20Kirron%20Kher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20last%20month%E2%80%99s%20mayoral%20polls%2C%20a%20joint%20candidate%20of%20the%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20was%20the%20favourite%20to%20win%20the%20post%20of%20Chandigarh%20mayor%20since%20both%20parties%20jointly%20had%20the%20support%20of%2020%20councillors%2C%20five%20more%20than%20that%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20BJP%20candidate%20Manoj%20Sonkar%20became%20new%20city%20mayor%20after%20Masih%20declared%20eight%20votes%20of%20opposition%20candidate%20invalid.%20Viral%20videos%20purportedly%20showed%20him%20rigging%20the%20ballots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20latest%20tally%20after%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20defection%20has%20increased%20to%2017%2C%20along%20with%20one%20additional%20vote%20of%20its%20MP%20(that%20is%2018%20now).%20With%20the%20Akali%20Dal%20councillor%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20it%20now%20enjoys%20the%20potential%20of%20securing%2019%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20opposition%20support%20has%20reduced%20to%2017%2C%20with%2010%20now%20belonging%20to%20AAP%20and%20the%20original%20seven%20of%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20now%20has%20the%20edge%20over%20the%20Congress%20and%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20changing%20political%20equation%20between%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20may%20also%20benefit%20BJP.%20During%20last%20month%E2%80%99s%20polls%2C%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20had%20managed%20to%20stitch%20up%20an%20alliance%20as%20they%20are%20both%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20Congress%20will%20indeed%20go%20for%20an%20alliance%20with%20AAP%20for%20the%20re-poll%20considering%20that%20the%20latter%20has%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20contest%20the%20Chandigarh%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708313040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F19085122%2FGGoxsalWMAAEL_a-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchandigarh-mayoral-polls-manoj-sonkar-supreme-court-aap%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20AAP%20councillors%20have%20jumped%20ship%20to%20turn%20the%20tides%20in%20favour%20of%20BJP%2C%20sources%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchandigarh-mayoral-polls-manoj-sonkar-supreme-court-aap%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20who%20won%20bid%20for%20plot%20linked%20to%20Dawood%20Ibrahim%20yet%20to%20pay%20up%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708312861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107807767%2Cimgsize-432737.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fman-who-won-plot-linked-to-dawood-yet-to-pay-up%2Farticleshow%2F107807530.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20lawyer%20Ajay%20Srivastava%20won%20two%20bids%20during%20the%20Jan%205%20auction%20of%20Ratnagiri%20propertie