r%20one%20dedicated%20to%20his%20two%20work%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20resume%20that%20got%20him%20the%20job%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221224%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Henry%20Wang's%20resume%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d2beffa3bd891424f85410%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221402%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWang%20used%20this%20resume%20to%20apply%20to%2C%20and%20land%20an%20offer%20at%20Google%20in%202013.%3Cp%3EHenry%20Wang%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EResume%20mistakes%20Wang%20made%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20roughly%2010%20years%20on%2C%20Wang%20reexamined%20that%20resume%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20says%20he'd%20do%20some%20things%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20back%2C%20I%20think%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20story%20to%20my%20resume.%20Right%20now%2C%20I'm%20just%20listing%20where%20I%20went%20to%20school%2C%20what%20my%20experiences%20were%20without%20really%20conveying%20what's%20the%20story%20that%20I%20want%20to%20tell%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20said%20about%20his%202013%20resume.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20he%20would%20change%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeclutter%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20look%20at%20this%2C%20my%20eyes%20kind%20of%20hurt.%20There's%20a%20lot%20of%20text%20and%20its%20all%20very%20packed%20together.%20I%20could%20use%20a%20more%20clean%20font%20that%20is%20easy%20to%20read%2C%20like%20Arial%2C%20Open%20Sans%20or%20Lato%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMinimize%20the%20work%20for%20the%20recruiter%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20have%20an%20introduction%20blurb%20about%20myself%20so%20the%20recruiter%20or%20interviewer%20does%20not%20have%20to%20read%20through%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20summarize%20my%20experience%20into%20two%20to%20three%20sentences%20at%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20so%20it's%20almost%20like%20a%20mini%20cover%20letter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELead%20with%20the%20new%3A%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3EAt%20this%20time%2C%20I%20had%20already%20been%20working%20two%20years%2C%20which%20means%20I%20could%20move%20education%20below%20and%20lead%20with%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShow%20your%20accomplishments%2C%20not%20your%20work%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWang%20said%20he'd%20focus%20less%20on%20listing%20tasks%2C%20and%20more%20on%20explaining%20how%20his%20tasks%20became%20accomplishments.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20for%20litigation%20paralegal%2C%20I%20would%20have%20a%20short%20blurb%20saying%2C%20'Managed%20and%20owned%20legal%20workflow%20for%20high%20profile%20family%20law%20cases%20from%20discovery%20to%20trial%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETailor%20for%20what%20you%20want%3A%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3EPick%20your%20battles%20%E2%80%94%20not%20every%20single%20work%20experience%20is%20going%20to%20be%20equal%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20said.%20Because%20he%20was%20applying%20for%20a%20policy%20role%20at%20Google%2C%20he%20says%20he%20should%20have%20emphasized%20his%20policy%20experience%20over%20his%20time%20in%20community%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20all%20negative%2C%20though.%20%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20I%20appreciate%20about%20this%20resume%20is%20that%20even%20though%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20information%2C%20I%20over%20communicated%20rather%20than%20under-communicated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20worked%20at%20Google's%20policy%20division%20and%20later%20as%20a%20product%20marketing%20manager.%20He%20left%20the%20company%20in%202017%20and%20now%20runs%20his%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40thegooglepmm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebusiness%3C%2Fa%3E%20consulting%20AI%20and%20crypto%20startups.%3C%2F