%20him%20from%20BJP%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708310879000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107808829%2Cimgsize-842641.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fthane%2Fshiv-sena-leader-aaditya-thackeray-challenges-ekanth-shinde-to-fight-election-from-thane-district%2Farticleshow%2F107806220.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fthane%2Fshiv-sena-leader-aaditya-thackeray-challenges-ekanth-shinde-to-fight-election-from-thane-district%2Farticleshow%2F107806220.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%3A%20An%20%2418%20Big%20Mac%20Meal%20Is%20Bad%20For%20America%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20meal%20I%20had%20as%20an%20American%20citizen%20was%20a%20Big%20Mac.%20This%20was%20in%20September%202013%2C%20and%20it%20cost%20less%20than%20%245%20at%20a%20McDonald's%20near%20the%20downtown%20Manhattan%20courthouse%20where%20the%20naturalization%20ceremony%20had%20taken%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20no%20expectation%20of%20enjoying%20it%3A%20I%20like%20my%20hamburgers%20greasy%20and%20flavorful%20and%20find%20Big%20Macs%20too%20dry%20and%20bland.%20But%20a%20McDonald's%20was%20close%20at%20hand%2C%20and%20a%20burger%20was%20the%20most%20appropriate%20way%20to%20commemorate%20a%20uniquely%20American%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20was%20in%20New%20York%2C%20I%20could%20have%20chosen%20from%20any%20number%20of%20pricey%20patties-in-a-bun.%20My%20friend%2C%20gastronomic%20guru%20and%20Bloomberg%20Opinion%20colleague%20Howard%20Chua-Eoan%20had%20once%20taken%20me%20to%20lunch%20at%20DB%20Bistro%20Moderne%20in%20midtown%2C%20where%20Chef%20Daniel%20Boulud's%20burger%2C%20made%20from%20a%20combination%20of%20short%20ribs%2C%20ground%20prime%20rib%2C%20foie%20gras%20and%20a%20hint%20of%20truffles%2C%20cost%20%2429.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20me%2C%20it%20is%20the%20cheap%20hamburger%20that%20is%20the%20archetypal%20American%20food%2C%20at%20once%20a%20national%20culinary%20quintessence%20and%20an%20instrument%20of%20international%20soft%20power%20-%20right%20up%20there%20with%20blue%20jeans%20and%20cola.%20It%20is%20also%20America's%20favorite%20dish%3A%20We%20eat%20an%20estimated%2050%20billion%20burgers%20a%20year%2C%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20which%20are%20made%20by%20affordable%20restaurant%20chains%20like%20McDonald's%20and%20Burger%20King.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20millions%20of%20Americans%20whose%20idea%20of%20dining%20out%20is%20a%20meal%20at%20one%20of%20those%20restaurants%2C%20it%20is%20their%20%26quot%3Bthird%20place.%26quot%3B%20That%20term%20was%20coined%20by%20sociologist%20Ray%20Oldenburg%20to%20describe%20the%20social%20environment%20where%20people%20are%20most%20likely%20to%20spend%20time%2C%20after%20home%20and%20work.%20This%20may%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20to%20those%20who%20live%20in%20big%20cities%2C%20where%20there%20are%20other%20third%20places%20-%20parks%2C%20coffee%20shops%2C%20et%20al.%20-%20and%20where%20a%20McDonald's%20is%20merely%20a%20collection%20point%20for%20a%20takeaway%20meal.%20But%20in%20smaller%20towns%2C%20and%20especially%20in%20poor%20and%20middle-income%20neighborhoods%2C%20a%20McDonald's%20can%20also%20serve%20as%20a%20community%20center%2C%20where%20people%20build%20and%20foster%20physical%20social%20networks.%20It%20can%20be%20a%20public%20square%20where%20people%20break%20free%20from%20their%20social%20media%20bubbles%20and%20encounter%20a%20wider%20range%20of%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20we%20should%20pay%20attention%20when%20Americans%20get%20all%20hot%20and%20bothered%20about%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20eating%20our%20favorite%20dish%20at%20their%20favorite%20place.%20An%20image%20from%20a%20Darien%2C%20Connecticut%2C%20McDonald's%20rest%20stop%20last%20July%20went%20viral%20because%20it%20showed%20that%20a%20Big%20Mac%20combo%20meal%20was%20priced%20at%20%2418.%20In%20November%2C%20an%20older%20video%20showing%20a%20%2416%20receipt%20for%20a%20smoky%20double%20quarter%20pounder%20BLT%2C%20a%20large%20fries%2C%20and%20a%20large%20Sprite%20from%20a%20McDonald's%20in%20Post%20Falls%2C%20Idaho%2C%20resurfaced%20on%20TikTok%20and%20went%20viral%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(It%20is%20worth%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20prices%20of%20burgers%20in%20chain%20stores%20can%20vary%20widely.%20According%20to%20the%20Council%20for%20Community%20and%20Economic%20Research%2C%20the%20retail%20price%20for%20a%20basic%20McDonald's%20quarter%20pounder%20last%20summer%20ranged%20from%20%243.79%20in%20Cedar%20Falls%2C%20Iowa%2C%20to%20%248.09%20in%20Billings%2C%20Montana.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerns%20about%20the%20price%20of%20hamburgers%20have%20risen%20in%20tandem%20with%20the%20broader%20worries%20about%20food%20inflation.%20And%20the%20anxiety%20hasn't%20been%20assuaged%20by%20the%20argument%20that%20it%20indicates%20a%20fall%20in%20income%20inequality%20because%20better%20pay%20for%20fast-food%20workers%20has%20contributed%20to%20the%20price%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBurger%20chains%20are%20anxious%2C%20too.%20For%20now%2C%20sales%20and%20profits%20remain%20robust%20-%20but%20that's%20because%20the%20price%20increases%20have%20compensated%20for%20a%20slowdown%20in%20customer%20traffic.%20To%20keep%20'em%20coming%2C%20burger%20joints%20have%20launched%20new%20marketing%20campaigns%2C%20some%20of%20them%20quite%20desperate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20is%20sending%20the%20Hamburglar%20on%20a%20promotional%20road%20trip%2C%20and%20the%20Big%20Mac%20is%20getting%20a%20big%20makeover.%20Burger%20King%20is%20hoping%20you'd%20be%20more%20inclined%20to%20visit%20one%20of%20its%20restaurants%20if%20the%20person%20at%20the%20till%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20rule!%26quot%3B%20and%20handed%20you%20a%20cardboard%20crown.%20In%20a%20more%20restrained%20approach%2C%20Wendy's%2C%20the%20third-largest%20burger%20chain%2C%20is%20counting%20on%20Cinnabon%20rolls%20to%20lure%20customers%20to%20breakfast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20bells%20and%20whistles%20-%20and%20somewhat%20more%20juicy%20patties%20-%20won't%20turn%20the%20tide.%20The%20American%20burger%20owes%20its%20iconic%20status%2C%20above%20all%2C%20to%20being%20inexpensive.%20McDonald's%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Chris%20Kempczinski%20acknowledged%20as%20much%20on%20an%20earnings%20call%20earlier%20this%20month%20when%20he%20said%20customers%20who%20make%20less%20than%20%2445%2C000%20a%20year%20are%20feeling%20the%20price%20pressure.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20an%20industry%20standpoint%2C%20we%20actually%20saw%20that%20cohort%20decrease%20in%20the%20most%20recent%20quarter%2C%20particularly%20I%20think%20as%20eating%20at%20home%20has%20become%20more%20affordable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKempczinski%20said%20the%20company%20will%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Baffordability%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Babsolute%20price%20point%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20temporary%20deals%20in%20the%20months%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20solution%20is%20not%20only%20important%20to%20the%20profit%20margins%20of%20restaurants.%20If%20fewer%20Americans%20are%20going%20to%20their%20third%20spaces%2C%20there%20will%20be%20consequences%20for%20society%20at%20large.%20For%20one%2C%20at%20a%20time%20of%20profound%20political%20division%2C%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20polarizing%20influences%20of%20an%20election%20year%2C%20we%20may%20need%20our%20third%20places%20more%20than%20ever%20-%20and%20a%20side%20of%20fries%20couldn't%20hurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2F