0forward%20with%20the%20'Delhi%20Chalo'%20march%20on%20February%2021%20adding%20that%20the%20discussion%20will%20also%20be%20held%20on%20the%20proposal%20proposed%20by%20the%20government%20on%20MSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20have%20discussions%20on%20the%20proposal%20by%20the%20govt%20in%20the%20next%20two%20days...The%20govt%20will%20also%20deliberate%20on%20the%20other%20demands...We%20will%20continue%20with%20the%20'Delhi%20Chalo'%20march%20on%20Feb%2021%20if%20there%20is%20no%20result%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pandher%20said%20while%20addressing%20the%20media%20after%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20meeting%20between%20protesting%20farmer%20unions%20and%20Union%20Ministers%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20the%20government%20and%20farmers'%20unions%20would%20try%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20have%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20proposal%20by%20the%20govt%20and%20take%20opinions%20on%20it...The%20decision%20will%20be%20taken%20by%20today%20morning%2C%20evening%20or%20the%20day%20after...The%20ministers%20said%20that%20they%20will%20have%20discussions%20on%20the%20other%20demands%20after%20returning%20to%20Delhi...The%20discussions%20will%20be%20held%20on%20Feb%2019-20%20and%20the%20'Delhi%20Chalo'%20march%20scheduled%20for%20Feb%2021%20will%20be%20decided%20based%20on%20the%20discussions...Together%20(govt%20and%20the%20farmers'%20union)%20we%20will%20try%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Farmer%20leader%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%20said%20that%20the%20government%20has%20given%20us%20a%20proposal%2C%20which%20will%20be%20supervised%20and%20managed%20by%20two%20government%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20discuss%20the%20proposal%20by%20the%20government%20(on%20MSP)%20with%20our%20forums%20and%20experts%20and%20then%2C%20we%20will%20come%20to%20a%20conclusion...Our%20march%20(Delhi%20Chalo)%20will%20continue%20till%20the%20demands%20are%20met...Talks%20on%20several%20other%20demands%20need%20to%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dallewal%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dallewal%20further%20said%20that%20we%20had%20a%20detailed%20discussion%20on%20our%20(farmers')%20demands%20during%20the%20fourth%20round%20of%20talks%20with%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20has%20given%20us%20a%20proposal%2C%20which%20guarantees%20MSP%20on%20pulses%2C%20maize%20and%20cotton%2C%20which%20will%20be%20supervised%20and%20managed%20by%20two%20government%20agencies%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20SKM%20(Non-Political)%20leader%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%20after%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20meeting%20between%20protesting%20farmer%20unions%20and%20Union%20Ministers%20in%20Chandigarh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20asserted%20that%20they%20had%20a%20very%20positive%20and%20extensive%20discussion%20with%20representatives%20of%20farmers%20adding%20that%20the%20farmer%20leaders%20will%20announce%20their%20decision%20on%20the%20government%20proposals%20by%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government-promoted%20cooperative%20societies%20like%20NCCF%20(National%20Cooperative%20Consumers'%20Federation%20of%20India)%20and%20NAFED%20(National%20Agricultural%20Cooperative%20Marketing%20Federation%20of%20India)%20will%20form%20a%20contract%20for%20the%20next%205%20years%20and%20buy%20products%20from%20the%20farmers%20on%20MSP.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20limit%20on%20the%20quantity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agitating%20farmers%20from%20Punjab%20have%20raised%20various%20demands%20including%20an%20ordinance%20on%20ensuring%20legal%20guarantees%20for%20MSPs%20and%20loan%20waivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20sides%20--%20ministers%20and%20farmer%20leaders%20--%20had%20met%20earlier%20on%20February%208%2C%2012%20and%20