ups%20in%20the%20Netherlands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708249260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-the-hague-riots-eritreans_6459887.jpg%3F20240218095933%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Friots-break-out-between-rival-eritrean-groups-in-the-netherlands-13074671%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cars%20have%20been%20set%20on%20fire%20as%20rioting%20broke%20out%20between%20two%20rival%20groups%20of%20Eritreans%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20on%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A455%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Friots-break-out-between-rival-eritrean-groups-in-the-netherlands-13074671%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Friots-break-out-between-rival-eritrean-groups-in-the-netherlands-13074671%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Friots-break-out-between-rival-eritrean-groups-in-the-netherlands-13074671%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Interview%20%7C%20BJP%20Will%20Suffer%20its%20Biggest%20Ever%20Defeat%20in%202024%2C%20Says%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18131506%2FFeoRgx5UYAElkYC.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatna%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Amidst%20a%20series%20of%20switchovers%20from%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20leaders%20and%20parties%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20won%E2%80%99t%20make%20any%20difference%20as%20the%20people%20are%20angry%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20and%20they%20are%20not%20shifting%20anywhere.%20%3Cem%3ENeta%20idhar%20udhar%20jaate%20rahte%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Leaders%20keep%20on%20switching%20here%20and%20there).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20poor%20people%20are%20suffering%20from%20an%20unprecedented%20price%20rise%20and%20the%20throttling%20of%20their%20voice%20and%20fundamental%20rights%20with%20the%20misuse%20of%20power.%20The%20poor%2C%20youth%2C%20backward%20classes%2C%20Dalits%20and%20minorities%20are%20being%20subjected%20to%20the%20worst-ever%20cruelty.%20As%20a%20political%20party%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20biggest%20sin%20to%20desert%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20people%20when%20they%20are%20suffering%20the%20worst%20nightmare%20in%20their%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20president%20said%2C%20speaking%20exclusively%20to%20the%20this%20writer%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20Nitish%20Kumar%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Jayant%20Choudhary%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Ashok%20Chavan%20in%20Maharashtra%20switched%20over%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecifically%20asked%20about%20the%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20whose%20departure%20to%20the%20BJP%20led%20to%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20government%20in%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20Lalu%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EWah%20habitual%20bhagora%20hai.%20Apne%20aadat%20se%20lachaar%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(He%20is%20a%20habitual%20turncoat.%20He%20is%20the%20prisoner%20of%20his%20habit).%20People%20have%20understood%20him%3B%20they%20will%20punish%20him%20heavily.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties%20and%20leaders%20to%20stand%20for%20the%20causes%20of%20people%20when%20they%20are%20suffering%20the%20worst-ever%20tyranny%20and%20oppression.%20I%20have%20never%20compromised%20with%20communal%20and%20oppressive%20forces%20and%20will%20never%20do%20it%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20challenge%20they%20(the%20BJP)%20pose%20before%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lalu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwave%E2%80%9D%20in%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20favour%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20RJD%20boss%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20all%20nonsense.%20The%20so-called%20wave%20is%20only%20in%20the%20media%20that%20they%20(the%20BJP)%20have%20captured.%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20every%20molecule%20of%20our%20existence%2C%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20used%20to%20create%20a%20%E2%80%98wave%E2%80%99%20for%20electoral%20gains.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20media%2C%20deviating%20from%20its%20work%20to%20raise%20and%20debate%20unprecedented%20unemployment%2C%20rising%20disparity%20in%20society%2C%20misuse%20of%20power%20and%20subjugation%20of%20the%20democratic%20institutions%20as%20never%20before%2C%20untold%20suffering%20of%20the%20farmers%20and%20farm-labourers%2C%20and%20unabated%20crackdown%20on%20the%20voices%20of%20dissent%2C%20is%20fanning%20hatred%20and%20creating%20divide%20among%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lalu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20warned%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20and%20parties%20across%20the%20country%20that%20they%20would%20suffer%20heavily%20for%20switching%20to%20the%20BJP%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20people%20have%20made%20up%20their%20mind%20to%20defeat%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%20%E2%80%9CTake%20it%20from%20me%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20suffer%20its%20biggest%20ever%20defeat%20in%20the%202024%20elections.%20People%20are%20full%20of%20disgust%20and%20resentment%20against%20the%20Modi%20government.%20They%20are%20waiting%20for%20their%20moment%20to%20dethrone%20it%E2%80%A6let%20the%20elections%20take%20place.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Robust%20INDIA%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalu%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CINDIA%20is%20in%20absolutely%20good%20health%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20flight%20of%20Nitish%20to%20the%20BJP%20has%20infused%20a%20fresh%20life%20in%20INDIA%20in%20Bihar.%20Done%20with%20Nitish%20%E2%80%93%20a%20perennial%20source%20of%20anxiety%20to%20any%20alliance%20he%20joins%20%E2%80%93%20we%20are%20left%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20Left%20parties%2C%20whose%20commitment%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20secularism%20and%20social%20justice%20is%20undiluted%20and%20unwavering.%20There%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20any%20problem%20at%20all%20on%20the%20issues%20of%20seat%20sharing%20and%20a%20common%20strategy%20to%20fight%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20NDA%20had%20won%2039%20out%20of%2040%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Bihar%20in%202019%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EBaar%20baar%20babul%20ke%20neeche%20aam%20nahin%20miltaa.%20Iss%20baar%20Bihar%20mein%20Bhajpa%20aur%20uske%20saathi%20kahin%20ke%20nahin%20rahegein%3C%2Fem%3E%20(One%20can%E2%80%99t%20get%20mangoes%20beneath%20the%20acacia%20tree%2C%20time%20and%20again.%20The%20BJP%20and%20its%20friends%20will%20be%20left%20with%20nothing%20to%20show%2C%20this%20time%20around).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Rahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20logon%20ko%20jagaane%20ka%20kaam%20kar%20rahe%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20awakening%20the%20people)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lalu%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20course%20of%20his%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyah%20Yatra%2C%20Rahul%20is%20talking%20about%20vicious%20unemployment%2C%20the%20BJP%20favouring%20the%20rich%20corporates%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20poor%2C%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20to%20the%20farmers%2C%20caste%20census%2C%20more%20quota%20for%20the%20backward%20classes%20and%20Dalits%20in%20government%20jobs%2C%20and%20back-breaking%20price%20rise.%20But%20the%20media%20instead%20of%20talking%20about%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20issues%20is%20hyping%20up%20the%20RSS-BJP%E2%80%99s%20narrative%2C%20bordering%20on%20crass%20communalism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20(Rahul)%20is%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20people%2C%20sharing%20their%20agony%20and%20distress.%20He%20is%20doing%20what%20a%20responsible%20opposition%20leader%20should%20do.%20He%20is%20on%20the%20right%20track.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18131346%2FF2tMqAwaEAEGQvx.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18131346%2FF2tMqAwaEAEGQvx.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18131346%2FF2tMqAwaEAEGQvx-300x180.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18131346%2FF2tMqAwaEAEGQvx-1024x614.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697704%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40laluprasadrjd%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalu%E2%80%99s%20son%20and%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20Bihar%20assembly%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20joined%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20yatra%20recently%20at%20Sasaram%20and%20drove%20a%20jeep%20with%20Rahul%20on%20the%20side%20seat%20for%20a%20stretch.%20Tejashwi%20launched%20a%20frontal%20attack%20on%20Modi%20for%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cneglect%20of%20the%20real%20issues%20facing%20the%20people%E2%80%9D%20and%20expressed%20his%20commitment%20to%20creating%20more%20jobs%20and%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExtending%20his%20whole-hearted%20support%20to%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20yatra%2C%20Tejashwi%20also%20recalled%20how%20Nitish%20had%20approached%20his%20parents%20(Lalu%20and%20Rabri%20Devi)%20with%20folded%20hands%20%E2%80%9Cbegging%20to%20save%20his%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20on%20the%20plea%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20splitting%20it%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20recent%20statement%20that%20his%20door%20was%20open%20for%20Nitish%2C%20Lalu%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C