ai%20reportedly%20made%20an%20attempt%20to%20halt%20an%20online%20lecture%20organised%20by%20a%20student%20body%2C%20featuring%20Magsaysay%20award%20winner%20and%20rights%20activist%20Bezwada%20Wilson.%20This%20comes%20a%20year%20after%20their%20previous%20effort%20to%20disrupt%20a%20similar%20lecture%20by%20researcher%20and%20human%20rights%20activist%20Harsh%20Mander.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fliberal-bastion-bid-to-gag-activist-bezwada-wilsons-lecture-at-tata-institute-of-social-sciences%2Fcid%2F2001244%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Students%20Organising%20Committee%2C%20an%20independent%20forum%20of%20TISS%20students%2C%20had%20informed%20the%20administration%20in%20December%202023%20about%20the%20proposed%20lecture%20by%20Wilson%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CBhagat%20Singh%20Memorial%20Lecture%E2%80%9D%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported%20that%20the%20institute%20issued%20an%20order%20a%20few%20weeks%20later%20that%20no%20programmes%20by%20students%20would%20be%20allowed%20till%20new%20guidelines%20were%20notified%20%E2%80%93%20though%20the%20date%20for%20the%20new%20guidelines%20was%20unspecified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20Friday%2C%20TISS%20authorities%20released%20a%20notice%20that%20the%20event%20was%20unauthorised.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20it%20has%20come%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20this%20Institute%20that%20some%20unauthorised%20student%20bodies%2F%20organisation%20claiming%20itself%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20TISS%20is%20going%20to%20organise%20an%20event%20titled%20as%20%E2%80%98Bhagat%20Singh%20Memorial%20Lecture%E2%80%99%20on%2017th%20February%2C%202024%20via%20online%2F%20offline%20mode%20from%2004%3A00%20p.m.%20onwards%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20regard%2C%20all%20the%20students%2C%20faculties%2C%20staff%20of%20the%20Institute%20and%20public%20at%20large%20are%20hereby%20informed%20that%20organising%20of%20such%20event%20has%20not%20been%20permitted%20by%20this%20Institute%20by%20any%20means%20and%20it%20has%20no%20relation%20with%20TISS.%20Hence%2C%20in%20view%20of%20above%2C%20all%20the%20concern%20is%20hereby%20requested%20to%20not%20to%20associate%20the%20above%20events%20with%20TISS%20in%20any%20capacity%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20event%20went%20ahead%20over%20Zoom%2C%20with%20Wilson%2C%20an%20activist%20against%20caste%20discrimination%20and%20manual%20scavenging%2C%20giving%20a%20lecture%20on%20the%20topic%20of%20%E2%80%9CHuman%20rights%20and%20constitutional%20values%20in%20contemporary%20times%3A%20Role%20of%20university%20and%20public%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20student%2C%20quoted%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20said%20that%20since%20the%20institute%20has%20yet%20to%20notify%20the%20new%20guidelines%2C%20the%20event%20could%20not%20be%20illegal%20and%20therefore%20it%20went%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20name%20of%20issuing%20new%20guidelines%2C%20the%20institute%20has%20been%20creating%20hurdles%20before%20students%E2%80%99%20activities.%20The%20students%20are%20a%20major%20stakeholder%20and%20have%20a%20say%20in%20the%20institute.%20Efforts%20to%20curb%20their%20voice%20are%20undemocratic%20and%20unacceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20another%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20report%2C%20citing%20three%20students%2C%20said%20TISS%20students%20had%20been%20organising%20the%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Memorial%20lecture%20since%202018.%20Earlier%20it%20was%20held%20in%20the%20institute%E2%80%99s%20amphitheatre%2C%20but%20it%20was%20shifted%20online%20in%202021%20and%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202023%2C%20TISS%20administration%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fharsh-mander-addresses-tiss-event-online-after-entry-ba