ologies%20Limited.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20step%20closer%20towards%20green%20solutions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20continues%20to%20inform%20that%20Hygenco%20builds%2C%20owns%2C%20and%20operates%20multiple%20green%20hydrogen%20facilities%20across%20the%20country%2C%20including%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20one%20of%20the%20few%20companies%20offering%20comprehensive%20360-degree%20techno-commercial%20solutions%20utilising%20green%20hydrogen.%20We%20offer%20cost-competitive%20alternatives%20for%20sustainable%20transportation.%20We%20are%20not%20just%20building%20infrastructure%3B%20we%20are%20shaping%20the%20future%20of%20clean%20energy%20and%20transportation%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20plants%20are%20designed%20with%20ambitious%20sustainability%20targets%20with%20the%20primary%20goal%20to%20responsibly%20conserve%20and%20source%20water%20for%20all%20our%20projects.%20With%20plants%20incorporating%20advanced%20software%20stack%2C%20Hygenco%E2%80%99s%20innovative%20approach%20enables%20efficiently%20consuming%20renewable%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Amit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20commitment%20towards%20leveraging%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20Hygenco%20has%20entered%20into%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20long-term%20green%20hydrogen%20purchase%20agreement%20with%20Jindal%20Stainless%20Limited%20(JSL).%20The%20project%20is%20a%20state-of-the-art%20green%20hydrogen%20facility%20located%20at%20JSL%20steel%20plant%20in%20Hisar%20that%20has%20a%20target%20to%20reduce%20carbon%20emissions%20considerably%20by%20about%202%2C700%20metric%20tonnes%20per%20annum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20plant%20is%20expected%20to%20produce%2075%20tonnes%20per%20annum%20of%20green%20hydrogen%20using%20roof-top%20and%20floating%20solar%20energy%20sources%20installed%20within%20the%20factory%20premises%2C%20contributing%20towards%20reducing%20carb