0just%20to%20pacify%20her%20mother%2C%20and%20if%20nothing%2C%20to%20make%20a%20friend.%20But%20in%20Prashant%2C%20she%20found%20her%20match.%20He%20had%20lost%20his%20wife%20to%20cancer%20and%20had%20three%20children.%20Vaishali%20found%20him%20%E2%80%9Ckind%2C%20compassionate%2C%20and%20caring%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20the%20first%20meeting%20led%20to%20many%20more%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20both%20eventually%20found%20companions%20who%20were%20in%20similar%20circumstances%20and%20could%20empathise%20with%20their%20respective%20situations.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20that%20after%20everything%2C%20I%20could%20still%20feel%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20for%20him%20%E2%80%94%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaishali%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EHumans%20Of%20Bombay%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20married%20for%2020%20years%20and%20are%20parents%20to%20five%20children%20and%20many%20grandchildren.%20Their%20children%20took%20time%20to%20accept%20the%20new%20family%2C%20but%20today%2C%20they%20are%20a%20solid%2C%20successful%20unit%20with%20plenty%20of%20love%20going%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Prashant%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20got%20married%2C%20she%20turned%20to%20Vaishali%20and%20asked%20her%20if%20she%20could%20call%20her%20%E2%80%9Cmom%E2%80%9D%2C%20since%20she%20had%20been%20just%20that%20for%20so%20many%20years.%20It%20was%20a%20moment%20Vaishali%20says%20she%20will%20cherish%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVaishali%20today%20is%20an%20advocate%20for%20other%20women%20to%20pursue%20their%20dreams%20and%20happiness%20after%20a%20tragedy.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20say%20that%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20that%20you%20are%20happy.%20You%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20care%20about%20society.%20I%20advise%20girls%20who%20have%20lost%20their%20husbands%20that%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20cue%20for%20them%20to%20stop%20living%20their%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20%E2%80%98I%20