f%20the%2018th-century%20palace.%20For%20Lakham%2C%20the%20part%20he%20thoroughly%20enjoyed%20was%20seeing%20life%20being%20breathed%20back%20into%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20place%20he%20calls%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%2C%20before%20India%20got%20independence%2C%20there%20used%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20would%20come%20to%20the%20palace%20to%20meet%20my%20grandfather.%20There%20would%20be%20activities%20going%20on%2C%20chatter%20and%20laughter.%20But%20in%20recent%20years%20my%20family%20were%20the%20only%20ones%20living%20here.%20Palaces%20are%20built%20for%20people.%20The%20human%20energy%20was%20missing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20the%20homestay%2C%20was%20an%20attempt%20at%20bringing%20it%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20deciding%20to%20restore%20the%20palace%20quarters%20to%20hosting%20their%20first%20guests%20in%20January%202023%2C%20the%20couple%20recount%20the%20four-year%20journey%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318930%2Fhomestays-in-srinagar-kashmir-scenic-views-of-dal-lake-mughal-tulip-gardens-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eiconic%20adventures%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20have%20had%20together.%20The%20most%20wonderful%20part%2C%20according%20to%20them%2C%20was%20inking%20friendships%20with%20the%20local%20artisans%20of%20Sawantwadi%20who%20were%20delighted%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20recall%20the%20legacy%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Eganjifa%3C%2Fem%3E%20art%20you%20were%20treated%20to%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20tale%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20thrilled%20to%20know%20that%20the%20art%20finds%20its%20purest%20expression%20in%20the%20palace%20hotel%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20facades%2C%20the%20decor%2C%20the%20cutlery%2C%20the%20furnishings%2C%20and%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20